{
  "application": "PBS",
  "details": {
    "software": [
      "gcc/6.2.0",
      "gsl/2.3",
      "boost/1.61.0",
      "bzip2/1.0.6",
      "python/3.5.3"

    "resource_requirements": {
      "walltime": "{{job_walltime}}",
      "memory": "{{job_memory}}",

      "{{ command }}",
      "{{ dap_command }}",
      "{{ frequency_filter }}",
      "{{ options }}",
      "{{ chromosome }}",
      "{{ sub_batches }}",
      "{{ sub_batch }}",
      "{{ grid }}",
      "{{ gene_annotation }}",
      "{{ genotype }}",
      "{{ genotype_metadata }}",
      "{{ phenotype }}",
      "{{ covariate }}",
      "{{ priors_folder }}",
      "{{ intermediate_folder }}",
      "{{ window }}",
      "{{ stats_name }}",
      "{{ parsimony }}",
      "{{ output }}"
    ]
  }
}
